{"tid":1508180,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「統計」九月一前，入嚟測試吓你的政治取向","createTime":"2019-08-26T12:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:29:17.000Z","uid":59832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a25d8c7a10e69a0db0aae30af92163a2d03387a3","tid":1508180,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:28:07.000Z","msg":"前傳：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191761\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191761</a><br />\n<br />\n衆所鳩知，經歷個兩個月嘅運動之後，唔少巴絲嘅政治取向都有所改變，不如試下對比返而家同69之前自己嘅政治取向有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politicalcompass.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politicalcompass.org&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=3addb16d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.politicalcompass.org</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個我諗大家都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://8values.github.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F8values.github.io&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=6511fdbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://8values.github.io</a><br />\n<br />\n四個維度，分別係 <span style=\"color: red;\">公平</span>&lt;&gt;<span style=\"color: green;\">市場</span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">國家</span>&lt;&gt;<span style=\"color: blue;\">世界</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">自由</span>&lt;&gt;<span style=\"color: teal;\">權威</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">傳統</span>&lt;&gt;<span style=\"color: purple;\">進步</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politiscales.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politiscales.net&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b9a3f541\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.politiscales.net</a>（有中文，但係得殘體）<br />\n<br />\n八個維度，詳情可以參考：<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://www.politiscales.net/zh_CN/help/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politiscales.net%2Fzh_CN%2Fhelp%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=98167e5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.politiscales.net/zh_CN/help/</a></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWBY4AU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWBY4AU.png&h=a5c8a2ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JguzCVT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJguzCVT.png&h=cde0c85a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3s5KAS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3s5KAS.png&h=fece6eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPfCAHw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPfCAHw.png&h=8eba688b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5845bb6d4871eac36fbd8e353c46776850d3902d","tid":1508180,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:28:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFi3Tp.jpg&h=1a5d1359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 和你塞 13:00 見</span></span> <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=ecfdb9a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=47ac4f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝